OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother largely dry and fine
OL,6,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Feeling a
OL,7,Flittle fresher than on Tuesday, with
OL,8,Fan easterly breeze, but still very
OL,9,Fwarm. Isolated showers from late
OL,10,Fafternoon, with a risk of thunder in
OL,11,Fthe west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright and very warm
OL,14,Fevening. Dry initially but an
OL,15,Fincreasing risk of showers moving
OL,16,Facross the region overnight, these
OL,17,Flocally heavy and thundery in places.
OL,18,FCooler than recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,169,160,301,260,100,100
