OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAny remaining showers soon
OL,6,Fclearing to the north early Thursday
OL,7,Fmorning, leaving a dry and sunny day
OL,8,Ffor many. Skies turning a little hazy
OL,9,Flater. Still feeling very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,12,Ffine and settled over the coming days,
OL,13,Fhowever it will turn cloudier from the
OL,14,Fwest at times, perhaps with some
OL,15,Fshowers on Thursday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fslowly returning to normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
